# AI Patterns — Vercel AI SDK + Gemini

## Vercel AI SDK — Core Hooks

Always use Vercel AI SDK hooks on the client. Never call AI Route Handlers with raw `fetch`.

```typescript
// ✅ Chat with streaming
"use client";

import { useChat } from "ai/react";

export function ChatArea() {
  const { messages, input, handleInputChange, handleSubmit, isLoading } = useChat({
    api: "/api/chat",
    onError: (error) => toast.error(error.message),
  });

  return (
    <div>
      {messages.map((msg) => (
        <MessageBubble key={msg.id} message={msg} />
      ))}
      <ChatInput
        value={input}
        onChange={handleInputChange}
        onSubmit={handleSubmit}
        isLoading={isLoading}
      />
    </div>
  );
}
```

