## Token Management

Always set `maxTokens` to prevent runaway costs. Tune per use case.

```typescript
// lib/constants/ai.constant.ts
export const AI_LIMITS = {
  CHAT_MAX_TOKENS: 1000,       // Regular chat message
  REVIEW_MAX_TOKENS: 2000,     // Code review (needs more output)
  SUMMARY_MAX_TOKENS: 500,     // Short summaries
  CONTEXT_MAX_CHUNKS: 5,       // Max RAG chunks to inject
  CONTEXT_MAX_CHARS: 3000,     // Max chars of RAG context
} as const;
```

