## Rules Summary

- ✅ All system prompts in `lib/ai/prompts.ts` — never inline
- ✅ Always set `maxTokens` in every AI call
- ✅ Always auth-check before AI route handler runs
- ✅ Use `useChat` / `useCompletion` from `ai/react` — never raw fetch
- ✅ Render AI messages with Markdown + syntax highlighting
- ✅ Rate limit every AI endpoint
- ✅ Save messages to DB in `onFinish` callback
- ❌ Never expose API keys to the client
- ❌ Never call Gemini API directly from Client Components
